      },
      "writtenOn": "2026-07-03T12:25:52Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "I went with GenerateV2 to indicate that this is not just intended to be a variation of Generate but a full replacement, and Generate will be deprecated and removed in time. GenerateV2 can do anything that Generate does, so I\u0027m reasonably OK with the name as is. Alternative suggestions?",
      "parentUuid": "b812feb8_6d15fecd",
      "revId": "6f59a356d0a7ec1fb5ac642b0223a27f7a041c6b",
